To run this code on the Precisely API, you would:

1. Send a POST request to `https://api.precisely.com/batch/v1/predictions` with the above JSON document in the body.
2. Set the header `Content-Type: application/json` to indicate that the payload is JSON data.
3. Include your Precisely API credentials as an authentication token in the header, e.g., `Authorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY`.
